text:
* “Rupees” or “₹” or “INR” or “Rs.” are to Indian Rupees, the official currency of the Republic of India;
* “US Dollar” or “USD” or “US$” or “$” are to United States Dollar, the official currency of the United States of America;
* “Mauritian Rupee” or “MUR” are to Mauritian Rupee, the official currency of the Republic of Mauritius
